{"id":386976,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/35/63/356378.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"靠谱人生茶话会","groupHref":"/group/boring","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/03/364.jpg","message":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/%E5%8C%97%E9%BD%8A%E6%9B%B8/%E5%8D%B710#%E9%A6%AE%E7%BF%8A%E7%8E%8B\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">北齊書/卷10</a><br><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E9%AB%98%E6%B6%A6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">馮翊王 潤</a>，字子澤，神武第十四子也。……潤美姿儀，年十四五，母鄭妃與之同寢，<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">有穢雜之聲</span>。<br><span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">这是开亲妈滴大车<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/70.gif\" smileid=\"109\" alt=\"(bgm93)\">这位郑母是什么人呢？<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"></span><br><a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/%E5%8C%97%E5%8F%B2/%E5%8D%B7014#%E8%A0%95%E8%A0%95%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">北史/卷014</a><br><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/%E9%84%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%BB%8A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">馮翊太妃鄭氏，名大車</a>，嚴祖妹也。初為魏廣平王妃。遷鄴後，<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AB%98%E6%AC%A2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">神武</a>納之，寵冠後庭，生馮翊王潤。神武之征劉蠡升，<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AB%98%E6%BE%84\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">文襄</a><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">蒸於大車</span>。<br><span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">字面意义上的大车<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/70.gif\" smileid=\"109\" alt=\"(bgm93)\"></span><br><span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">文襄是谁呢？</span><span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">是神武他儿子。</span><br>蠕蠕公主者……公主性嚴毅，一生不肯華言。……神武崩，文襄從蠕蠕國法，<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">蒸公主</span>……<br>琅邪公主名玉儀，魏高陽王斌庶生妹也。初不見齒，<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">為孫騰妓</span>，騰又放棄。文襄遇諸途，<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">悅而納之</span>……<br><span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">文宣是次子。</span><br>彭城太妃爾硃氏……及文宣狂酒，<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">將無禮於太妃</span>……<br>文襄敬皇后元氏……及天保六年，文宣……曰：「<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">吾兄昔奸我婦，我今須報。</span>」乃淫於後。其高氏女婦，無親疏皆使左右<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">亂交</span>之於前。以葛為絙，令魏安德主騎上，使人推引之。又命胡人苦辱之<span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">凌辱</span>。帝又自呈露，以示群下。<span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">裸奔</span><br>……<br>传奇人物很多，武成皇后是一位佼佼者<br>武成皇后胡氏，安定胡延之女。……武成<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">寵倖</span>和士開<span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">武成皇帝和和士开搞基</span>。每與後<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">握槊</span>，因此與後<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">奸通</span><span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">皇后干了和士开</span>。自武成崩後，數出詣佛寺，<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">又與沙門曇獻通</span><span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">找了个和尚继续啪啪啪</span>。布金錢於獻度下，又掛寶裝胡床於獻屋壁，武成平生之所禦也。乃置百僧於內殿，托以聽講，<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">日夜與曇獻寢處</span>。……齊亡，入周，<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">恣行奸穢</span>。<span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">亡国后也不影响武成皇后的性自由</span><span class=\"text_mask\" style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">女权巅峰在南北朝？<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/70.gif\" smileid=\"109\" alt=\"(bgm93)\"></span> ","time":"2023-9-11 00:16","title":"枭雄之志的继承者们","userId":"ptsd","userName":"禁止左转","userSign":"(诸君，我喜欢战争)"}